reviewText: I was a fan of Ken's years ago.  I was looking for a comedy DVD as fall kick off for our women's group to enjoy some snacks & laughter for our first get together after summer break.  I think this DVD will work well.

Ken Davis proves he is still funny with a mix of old material and some new material. His delivery is great and his interaction with his audience is wonderful. We own every one of his DVD's and we pray he will be able to do more.

Love Ken Davis!  We wish the DVD description was more clear, though - these were almost the same jokes as on other DVDs.  Ken is always great entertainment, though, so this will make a nice gift to someone who hasn't seen him before.
This is truly a funny DVD--you'll find yourself laughing at real life experiences told in a very humerous, clean manner!  It's one of ther funniest speakers I've ever heard!
